snippet.title: Let's Play Star Trek Armada - 01 - Intro Sequence
snippet.description:
Let's see some action in space - yeah! With the Federation, the Borg, the Klingons and the Romulans!

See some of the spectacular special powers in action and watch as a Borg cube gets destroyed by a single blast - just like in the movies - not!
